Package common

Class BorrowReport

java.lang.Object
common.BorrowReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class BorrowReport extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a borrowing report for a genre in the library system. This class implements Serializable to support transmission between client and server.
